{"tid":2340412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"浙江省委書記：反壟斷是習近平為核心黨中央決策部署","createTime":"2020-12-25T12:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T03:04:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"734c1b22077defd9b50beddb46cf2e812067f639","tid":2340412,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"浙江省委書記袁家軍，今日召開省委經濟工作會議，強調反壟斷、反不正當競爭，是以習近平同志為核心的黨中央作出的決策部署，亦是完善社會主義市場經濟體制、推動高質量發展的內在要求。 <br />\n<br />\n對於市場監管總局對阿里巴巴集團涉嫌壟斷行為依法立案調查，金融管理部門亦將約談螞蟻集團，他強調，浙江平台經濟、線上經濟走在前列，今次反壟斷調查，是提升互聯網企業公平競爭意識及反壟斷合規意識的契機，亦是開啟平台經濟創新、有序及健康發展的機遇。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2372221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2372221&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=c73254f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2372221</a>"},{"pid":"5b82bf34f0e0d89107af6139cdd43949e6ef79f9","tid":2340412,"uid":34666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T12:18:37.000Z","msg":"共產黨壟斷呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8a7799acf418a001344e9761d56c60ed7ef27b","tid":2340412,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T12:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VstF2PT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVstF2PT.gif&h=32122299&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f54b4607a822b69aba5cb96355c11e1d40dafb82","tid":2340412,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9f1238a725ab312a8c3d99f649057eff959e73","tid":2340412,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:01:55.000Z","msg":"好,開始反政治壟斷未?"},{"pid":"41b136a071d73531d8a2aa74af38e7f184c00012",